{"tid":1631000,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［勿中計］請暫緩一切裝修行動","createTime":"2019-10-06T14:22:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T15:23:33.000Z","uid":162711,"like":15,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"09b5069d191ce8618a1f661b57a71e287d9a1acd","tid":1631000,"uid":162711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:22:37.000Z","msg":"而家咪撚再討論要裝修啲咩鋪頭<br />\n裝修去到呢個位係時候要停一停<br />\n而家開始<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">所有帶風向撚</span></span>，話要裝修乜乜柒柒<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">一律係鬼</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n記住我哋係文明嘅示威者，必要時勇武<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">同班冇腦暴力嘅藍絲/毅進仔係唔同！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n唔好係又裝修唔係又裝修，仲要搞到炒哂車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n裝修呢啲慢慢等個法案過咗都未遲<br />\n<br />\n唔知幾時有班風向撚/鬼<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"> 刻意將勇武極端化</span></span><br />\n<br />\n就係想食住個勢令到我哋班勇武仔仔愈嚟愈激進，搞到佢哋好似走火入魔真係變到暴徒咁，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">乘機和勇分化</span></span><br />\n<br />\n唔止裝修，總之連登就出現咗一大班<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">風向撚</span></span></span> 意圖分化，有啲又話港島遊行，有啲又話開花<br />\n<br />\n政府而家愈嚟愈束手無策，就開始派鬼滲透連登，各位手足要加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"958587fc3e46827826799b35105f44ab4cc5e984","tid":1631000,"uid":162711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:24:04.000Z","msg":"推1"},{"pid":"c8f96a4fde9507b8ae2281067a30c8cc21f4c3d3","tid":1631000,"uid":212554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:25:32.000Z","msg":"冷靜呀前線<br />\n一定要通過人權法"},{"pid":"ef1987f730eb6ae504ae9358fccb02dc764efd25","tid":1631000,"uid":162711,"like":0,"di